i\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係好驚<br />\n覺得自己玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"仲記得考core嗰排狀態非常差，幾乎日日翻屋企都喊，之後隔咗2個禮拜考elective習慣咗輕鬆咗，反而出黎成績好好多。心態真係決定好多嫁。（放榜分數比我expect既多5分）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家剩翻日子唔多，溫到既有限，倒不如真係好好開始調整生理時鐘，習慣6點起身7點幾8點操卷（dse都係8點幾考）<br />\nbtw 依家讀緊u，先發現其實一開始考得好唔好、入唔入到u，並唔係一件有咩大不了既事，識好多入到u既人浪費一年quit u retake rejupas，又識好多係asso奮鬥緊既同學，asso入大學其實容易過dse。你係有料既，平時aim開19/20分或以上，就算失手入唔到u，都可以入asso讀2年駁翻大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea8a29c66132f275c2d5c7ffcd702491547e89a","tid":1925772,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886e8a08df5d921686be87bc2fc28a18af9cf8c2","tid":1925772,"uid":277155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28378f930cd959eac62e48fc351a46200c3ff87a","tid":1925772,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"唔好溫書，溫past paper"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"所有科都係？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n因為你要知道會唔會有啲out-syl 或者考法唔同咗。<br />\n否則應該溫past paper先，有嘢唔明先睇返書或者問人。"},{"pid":"c14fe13d6a93202c00fff9a5963c07ce0aaafbf4","tid":1925772,"uid":277155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ea8a29c66132f275c2d5c7ffcd702491547e89a","tid":1925772,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886e8a08df5d921686be87bc2fc28a18af9cf8c2","tid":1925772,"uid":277155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28378f930cd959eac62e48fc351a46200c3ff87a","tid":1925772,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"唔好溫書，溫past paper"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"所有科都係？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n因為你要知道會唔會有啲out-syl 或者考法唔同咗。<br />\n否則應該溫past paper先，有嘢唔明先睇返書或者問