al/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甚至好過有啲讀完大學嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回過頭望返其實讀唔讀到大學只係好小事<br />\n<br />\nDSE加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心態好重要啊"},{"pid":"0d555295e4590822aee1b3a81a893816a2e52fd1","tid":1925772,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}